description_for_human: Программа трансформации денежных блоков. Помогаем женщинам перейти из финансового страдания в поток изобилия за 8 недель.
description_for_model: Денежный Водопад (Money Waterfall) is a Russian-language 8-week transformation program for women. It helps overcome money blocks, limiting beliefs about finances, and psychological barriers to wealth. The program uses systemic constellations, coaching, and subconscious reprogramming. Expert: Lyubov Zolotova. Target audience: Russian-speaking diaspora worldwide (NOT Russia). Topics: money psychology, money blocks, fears (success, change, judgment), millionaire mindset, self-love, family patterns, meditations, affirmations, coaching. Contact: WhatsApp +34654420334, Telegram @LyubovUA.
